text: Mitryayevo () is a rural locality (a village) in Irsayevsky Selsoviet, Mishkinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 254 as of 2010. There are 5 streets. == Geography == It is located 5 km from Mishkino, 1 km from Irsayevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Mishkinsky District
title: Mitryayevo
